e Divine Authenticity of the Book of Mormon\n | place=Richmond, Missouri\n | publisher=David Whitmer\n | year=1887\n | url=http://www.utlm.org/onlinebooks/address1.htm\n }}.\n{{refend}}\n\n{{Latter Day Saint movement}}\n{{LDS sects}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Church Of Christ (Latter Day Saints)}}\n[[Category:1830 establishments in New York (state)]]\n[[Category:Church of Christ (Latter Day Saints)| ]]\n[[Category:History of the Latter Day Saint movement]]\n[[Category:Kirtland, Ohio]]\n[[Category:Nauvoo, Illinois]]\n[[Category:Pre-succession crisis sects in the Latter Day Saint movement| ]]\n[[Category:Religious organizations established in 1830]]\n[[Category:Seneca County, New York]]\n[[Category:Ontario County, New York]]\n[[Category:Joseph Smith]]\n", "name_user": "Epachamo", "label": "safe", "comment": "Added note to future editors to address changes at the WP:LDSMOS", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Church_of_Christ_(Latter_Day_Saints)"}
